text: Morgunov () is a Russian masculine surname, its feminine counterpart is Morgunova. It may refer to *Aleksandr Morgunov (born 1995), Russian football midfielder *Lyubov Morgunova (born 1971), Russian long-distance runner *Nikita Morgunov (born 1975), Russian basketball player *Nina Morgunova (born 1951), Russian middle-distance runner *Sergey Morgunov (born 1993), Russian long jumper *Yevgeny Morgunov (1927–1999), Russian actor Category:Russian-language surnames
title: Morgunov
